          <li>Attempt to reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble any part of this website</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the normal operation of the website</li>
          <li>Infringe upon the intellectual property rights of others</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          When using this service, users should:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
          <li>Not distribute malware or engage in harmful activities</li>
          <li>Respect other users and the website's user experience</li>
          <li>Use website resources reasonably and avoid excessive requests</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Disclaimer</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          This website provides services "as is" without any express or implied warranties. We do not guarantee:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-gray-700">
          <li>Continuity or error-free operation of the service</li>
          <li>Absolute accuracy of solving results</li>
          <li>Completeness or timeliness of website content</li>
          <li>That the service will not be interrupted or terminated</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Limitation of Liability</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, we shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of this website.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Privacy Protection</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We value user privacy. For specific privacy handling practices, please refer to our <a href="/privacy-en" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Agreement Modifications</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We reserve the right to modify this agreement at any time. After modifications to the agreement, continued use of this service indicates your acceptance of the modified agreement.
