        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact Us</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          If you have any questions about this agreement, please contact us through the following means:
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Email: <a href="mailto:support@sliding-puzzle-solver.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@sliding-puzzle-solver.com</a>
